text: Sundale is an unincorporated community in Klickitat County, in the U.S. state of Washington. ==History== A post office called Sundale was established in 1915, and remained in operation until 1945. The community was named by the railroad. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Klickitat County, Washington Category:Unincorporated communities in Washington (state)
title: Sundale, Washington
